'''氫分子離子'''（{{chem|H|2|+}}），又称'''双氢离子'''，是最簡單的[[分子離子|分子離子]]，由兩個[[質子|質子]]和一個[[電子|電子]]組成。<ref>{{cite book |title = ''Principles of Modern Chemistry, Seventh Edition'' |author = David W. Oxtoby, H.P. Gillis, Alan Campion |publisher = Engage Learning |isbn = 9780840049315 |location = [[United_States_of_America|United States of America]]}}</ref>{{rp|99}}
它可以由一個中性的[[氫分子|氫分子]][[電離|電離]]而成。由于[[宇宙射线|宇宙射线]]，[[分子云|分子云]]中经常形成这种离子。
因為它只有一個電子，化學界對它兴趣很大。描述其结构的[[量子力学|量子力学]][[方程|方程]]可以以相对简单的方式得到解。1927年（量子力学中的波理论发表仅一年后），[[Øyvind_Burrau|Øyvind Burrau]]首次将其解出。

==物理性质==
{{chem|H|2|+}}中的键可以被描述为共价[[化学键|单电子键]]，形式上拥有0.5的[[键级|键级]]。<ref>{{Cite book|author=Clark R. Landis|author2=Frank Weinhold |title=Valency and bonding: a natural bond orbital donor-acceptor perspective |publisher=Cambridge University Press |location=Cambridge, UK |year=2005 |pages=91–92 |isbn=978-0-521-83128-4 }}</ref>  

离子的基态能量为-0.597 [[哈特里能量|哈特里能量]]。<ref>{{Cite journal | doi=10.1016/S0009-2614(97)00571-X| title=Nonadiabatic wavefunctions as linear expansions of correlated exponentials. A quantum Monte Carlo application to H2+ and Ps2| year=1997| last1=Bressanini| first1=Dario| last2=Mella| first2=Massimo| last3=Morosi| first3=Gabriele| journal=Chemical Physics Letters| volume=272| issue=5–6| pages=370–375| bibcode=1997CPL...272..370B}}</ref>

===同位素体===
氢分子离子拥有六种[[同位素体|同位素体]]，这来自氢其他[[同位素|同位素]]的原子核——即[[氘核|氘核]]（{{chem2|^{2}H(+)}}）或[[氚核|氚核]]（{{chem2|^{3}H(+)}}）——对一或两个质子（[[氕核|氕核]]）的取代。<ref name=fabr2009>{{cite journal | last1 = Fábri | first1 = Csaba | last2 = Czakó | first2 = Gábor | last3 = Tasi | first3 = Gyula | last4 = Császár | first4 = Attila G. | year = 2009 | title = Adiabatic Jacobi corrections on the vibrational energy levels of {{chem2|H2(+)}} isotopologues | journal = Journal of Chemical Physics | volume =  130| issue = 13| page =  134314| doi = 10.1063/1.3097327 | pmid = 19355739 }}</ref><ref name=scar2017>{{cite journal | last1 = Scarlett | first1 = Liam H. | last2 = Zammit | first2 = Mark C. | last3 = Fursa | first3 = Dmitry V. | last4 = Bray | first4 = Igor | year = 2017 | title = Kinetic-energy release of fragments from electron-impact dissociation of the molecular hydrogen ion and its isotopologues | journal = Physical Review A | volume = 96 | issue = 2| page = 022706 | doi = 10.1103/PhysRevA.96.022706 | bibcode = 2017PhRvA..96b2706S | doi-access = free }}</ref>

* {{chem2|H2(+)}} = {{chem2|^{1}H2(+)}}（最常见）<ref name=fabr2009/><ref name=scar2017/>
* {{chem2|[DH](+)}} = {{chem2|[^{2}H^{1}H](+)}}（氘氢离子）<ref name=fabr2009/>
* {{chem2|D2(+)}} = {{chem2|^{2}H2(+)}}（双氘离子）<ref name=fabr2009/><ref name=scar2017/>
* {{chem2|[TH](+)}} = {{chem2|[^{3}H^{1}H](+)}}（氚氢离子）
* {{chem2|[TD](+)}} = {{chem2|[^{3}H^{2}H](+)}}（氚氘离子）
* {{chem2|T2(+)}} = {{chem2|^{3}H2(+)}}（双氚离子）<ref name=scar2017/>

